Ranger Help for: impale
=======================

SYNTAX:      impale <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     90
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to deliver a devastating piercing attack,
driving their weapon deep into the target. The Ranger must be wielding
a pierce-type weapon (spear, dagger, rapier, etc.) to perform this
skill. Impale deals very high pierce damage and is one of the strongest
single-hit melee attacks available to Rangers. The damage scales with
the Ranger's strength and weapon proficiency.
